# ===========================================================================
# Tree Harness 环境变量示例
# ===========================================================================
# 用法：复制本文件为 .env，填入你的真实 API 配置
#   cp .env.example .env
#
# 项目通过 RealLLMClient.from_env(provider) 读取环境变量：
#   - provider="qwen"     → 读取 QWEN_*
#   - provider="deepseek" → 读取 DEEPSEEK_*
# 两个 provider 二选一即可，代码默认使用 qwen。
# 切换 provider 需在调用处修改 from_env(...) 的参数。
#
# 约束 (DESIGN.md):
#   - temperature = 0 (确定性输出)
#   - 相同输入全量缓存，重复调用不产生额外开销
# ===========================================================================

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Qwen (默认 provider) — 阿里云 DashScope OpenAI 兼容接口
# 申请 key: https://dashscope.console.aliyun.com/
# 可选模型: qwen-plus / qwen-max / qwen-turbo 等
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
QWEN_API_KEY=sk-your-qwen-api-key-here
QWEN_BASE_URL=https://dashscope.aliyuncs.com/compatible-mode/v1
QWEN_MODEL=qwen-plus

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# DeepSeek — DeepSeek OpenAI 兼容接口
# 申请 key: https://platform.deepseek.com/
# 可选模型: deepseek-chat / deepseek-reasoner 等
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
DEEPSEEK_API_KEY=sk-your-deepseek-api-key-here
DEEPSEEK_BASE_URL=https://api.deepseek.com/v1
DEEPSEEK_MODEL=deepseek-chat
